I'm joining @Shopify.

@carlrivera and @maggiefost have a bold plan for design next year. I'm here for it.

I'm part of a newly-formed group in the brand design studio that's leading special projects across various teams.

One of my favourite little details in the new COLLINS website is this responsive border-radius.

--margin: calc((100% - var(--max-width)) / 2);
border-radius: clamp(1rem, calc(1.5rem - var(--margin)), 1.5rem);

<https://t.co/mokwcgE2eM>
